  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>That works great!

One minor thing is that I had a tiny bit of trouble with the ui.  There's a
"save all projects" button in the lower right hand corner.  So I think the page
is "button = action" oriented.  But to save the order, you have to click on a
link above the list of projects.

So when I finished moving projects around, I went to click on the "save all
projects" button, which didn't do anything because it was disabled.  Then I had
to read everything on the screen to figure out what to do next.

Thought I would mention it.  &lt;disclaimer&gt;I'm just one data point and I don't do
ui design, but if others have similar issues it might be worth looking
into.&lt;/disclaimer&gt;</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
