  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I've got a bunch of projects in my openhatch account.  There are a handful of
them that I'm currently working on and the rest I've worked on in the past, but
I'm not working on them now (and some of them I probably won't work on again).

It'd be nice to be able to order the projects listed either:

1. completely--I get to move them around and specify the order they show up on
the page, or
2. in two groups: active and unactive

The use case is this: if I was able to order the projects, then whoever looked
at my page would see the "important" projects at the top.  If I had a lot of
projects (like Joey Hess), then someone wouldn't have to skim through all the
projects to get a feel for what I'm working on.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
